    "It is a method for weakly supervised learning with incomplete, inexact, and inaccurate supervision.",
    "The main idea of the framework is to use an unbiased and statistically efficient risk estimator that is applicable Page 19 of 41 66 to various weak supervision.",
    "By decomposing the loss function into a label-independent term and a label-dependent term, it is found out that only the latter is influenced by the weak supervision and is related to the centroid of the entire dataset.",
    "Focuses on statistical efficiency, in addition to estimation unbiasedness.",
    "CEGE can cover many weak supervised problems, and accommodate many loss functions, and can use SVM and neural networks for classification."
